useState rules
- whenever we update a state value which is dependent on its prev values always use a callback func which accepts prev value


-- state management for a complex object

In order to manage complex objects, react provides a hook called useReducer

syntax

const [state, dispatch] = useReducer(reducerFunc, complexObjectState);
